DOVER CHARTERS 397

we, the said Thomas, William, and Roger Wood, have to these presentes put to our seals3 and for that our seals is not to all men knowen, Therefore we have cauesed for the better testymony thereos the sealle off office of mayiralty to thee presentes to be affyxed.

Dated the xxviffl daye of Julii anno regni Regine nostre Elizabeth, primo.

One scal remains.
